Graphique de lecd en fonction de laire

chart(zooplankton_sub, formula = ecd ~ area %col=% perimeter) +
  geom_point(na.rm= TRUE) 

library(ggridges)

primtre selon les classes

chart(zooplankton_sub, class ~ perimeter %fill=% class %alpha=% class) +
  geom_density_ridges() 
## Picking joint bandwidth of 0.738

axe mineur de lellipsode en fonction de la classe

chart(zooplankton_sub, formula = min ~ class %fill=% class) + 
  geom_violin() + 
  coord_flip()

chart(zooplankton_sub, ~ elongation %alpha=% class) + 
  geom_histogram(bins=30) 

chart(zooplankton_sub,formula=~ elongation %col=% class)+ 
  geom_density()

chart(zooplankton_sub, formula= compactness ~ transparency %alpha=% class) + 
  geom_point(na.rm = TRUE)

chart(zooplankton_sub, formula = ~ circularity) + 
  geom_density()

chart(zooplankton_sub, formula = ~ transparency) + 
  geom_density()

chart(zooplankton_sub, formula=~mean %col=% class %alpha=% class) + 
  geom_histogram()
